overview: Can you believe there is ANOTHER NEW volume of “Lost & Found Video Night”?! Well, there is and here it is, “Lost & Found Video Night Vol. 17”! Prepare for rare TV appearances from Rip Taylor, Vincent Price, OJ Simpson, Paul Lynde, Andy Warhol & Edie Sedgwick! Watch rare performances & videos by Blondie, Dr. Octagon, Spacemen 3, Fear, David Bowie & more! Prepare for more public access weirdness, forgotten bizarro TV commercials, brilliant stand up from Bill Hicks, David Lynch carving a styrofoam dildo and more, more, more!
title: Lost & Found Video Night Vol. 17
